div.index-page
    section
        h2 Learn more about Cats (
            |
            span.catapi-link according to#{" "}
                |
                a(href="https://thecatapi.com" target="_blank") thecatapi.com
            | )

        p According to wikipedia, the cat (Felis catus) is a domestic species of small#{" "}
            | carnivorous mammal. It is the only domesticated species in the family #{" "}
            | Felidae and is often referred to as the domestic cat to distinguish it #{" "}
            | from the wild members of the family. A cat can either be a house cat,#{" "}
            | a farm cat or a feral cat; the latter ranges freely and avoids human#{" "}
            | contact. Domestic cats are valued by humans for companionship and their#{" "}
            | ability to kill rodents. About 60 cat breeds are recognized by various#{" "}
            | cat registries.

    section
        p The cats have been grouped into breeds and categories. The breeds section provides some useful information about cats,#{" "}
            | while the categorie section shows some cool pictures (Pick your favourite cats' pictures).
        
        div.breeds-categories-section
            section.breeds-section
                h3 Breeds 
                ul 
                    each breed in listOfBreeds
                        li: a(href=`/breeds/${breed.id}`) #{breed.name}
                
            section.categories-section
                h3 Categories  
                ul 
                    each categorie in listOfCategories
                        li: a(href=`/categories/${categorie.id}`) #{categorie.name}